476
00:40:18,720 --> 00:40:21,360
I to sam objavio tek 2021.

477
00:40:21,600 --> 00:40:22,240
u promjesecu.

478
00:40:22,320 --> 00:40:24,160
Zamislite, koliko dugo trebao.

479
00:40:24,240 --> 00:40:27,360
Zamislite kako sam šupak bio da nisam ljudima se ni javio.

480
00:40:27,440 --> 00:40:29,200
Nisam im ni rekao da neću objaviti.

481
00:40:32,240 --> 00:40:33,360
Nakon nekoliko godina.

482
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:35,680
Od 2018.

483
00:40:35,840 --> 00:40:36,480
