Nisam bio, osjećao sam ogroman pritisak od osude okolina.

487
00:40:49,200 --> 00:40:50,240
Da, da, nije mala stvar.

488
00:40:51,360 --> 00:40:52,000
Ogromna stvar.

489
00:40:53,200 --> 00:40:56,880
